** Real Time SQL Monitoring

** Rael Time Database Operation Monitoring
  - single    DB operation (SQL or PL/SQL)
  - composite DB operation
    - single session
    - multiple concurrent sessions

  - OCIAttrSet, OCIAppCtxSet
  - JAVA -> setClientInfo
  - ORA_DBOP environment

  - Statement Level
    --+ MONITOR
    --+ NO_MONITOR

  - Database Operation Level
    - DBMS_SQL_MONITOR
      - begin_opeation
      - end_operation
      - report_sql_monitor
      - report_sql_monitor_list

  - System Level
    - longer than 5 seconds
    - parallel executions

  - V$SQL_MONITOR
  - V$SQL_PLAN_MONITOR
  - DBA_HIST_ACTIVE_SESS_HISTORY

** Emergency Monitoring
  sqlplus -prelim / as sysdba
  SQL> oradebug setospid <os_pid>
  SQL> oradebug hanganalyze 3

** Real-Time ADDM
  - Audtomatic Database Diagnostic Monitor

  - select dbms_addm.real_time_addm_report () from dual;

  - @ rtaddmrpt


