*** Views
  - CDB_SERVICES

** New Features

*** Identity Colums
   - Columns specific sequence

   - <col> number generated always as identity
   - <col> number generated by default as identity
   - <col> number generated by default on null as identity (SQL*LOADER)
 

*** Invisible Columns

  - set colinvisible on


*** Partitioning
  - truncate cascade update index
  - create global partitioned index on non-partitioned table
  - partial indexing (an index only spawns some partitions)
    SQL Table> ... indexing on  ...
               ... indexing off ...
    SQL Index> ... indexing partial ...
               ... indexing full    ... (default)

